init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The story begins with a young man named Riku, who lives in a world where magic has long been forgotten.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He has been raised by his grandfather, a wizard, and has always dreamed of becoming a great wizard himself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He decided to go to the city of Faltra, where he had heard there were many people who could teach him about magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Riku's first day in Faltra is a disaster.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He made friends with a young girl named Selphie, who was a waitress at the bakery.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Riku and Selphie were overjoyed to be reunited, and they spent the evening talking and catching up.
